
        This file represents changes in the pixcon libraries that
        prevents backward compatibility w/ previous versions.

version 1.04
        anitroll -
                flight/buckey - removal of the "axis_x/y/z" attribute;
                        for flight, this was replaced by "orientation_mx"
                boid -  modified syntax for "yellow_alert"

version 1.05
        pixcon - remove "MORPH" option from polygon 2D texturing
        pixcon/anitroll - remove "luminate" option - "LUM" from
                .ilm files is used automaticly
        pixcon - removed SGI multiprocessor support (unable to
                support due to lack of access to platform)

